College Management Lightning Application (Salesforce LWC)
Step 1: Create Custom Objects

Create 2 Custom Objects:

1. Student Object

Label: Student
API Name: Student__c

Fields:

Field Label	Data Type
Student Name	Text
Roll Number	Number
Marks	Number
Email	Email
2. Faculty Object

Label: Faculty
API Name: Faculty__c

Fields:

Field Label	Data Type
Faculty Name	Text
Faculty ID	Number
Salary	Currency
Department	Picklist
Joining Date	Date

Department Picklist Values:

Computer
IT
Mechanical
Civil
AI&DS
Step 2: Create Validation Rules
Validation Rules for Student
1. Marks should be between 0 and 100
Rule Name:

Student_Marks_Validation

Formula:
OR(
    Marks__c < 0,
    Marks__c > 100
)
Error Message:
Marks must be between 0 and 100.
2. Roll Number must be greater than 0
Rule Name:

Student_RollNo_Validation

Formula:
Roll_Number__c <= 0
Error Message:
Roll Number must be greater than 0.
3. Email must contain @ symbol
Rule Name:

Student_Email_Validation

Formula:
NOT(CONTAINS(Email__c, "@"))
Error Message:
Email must contain @ symbol.
4. Student Name cannot be blank
Rule Name:

Student_Name_Validation

Formula:
ISBLANK(Student_Name__c)
Error Message:
Student Name cannot be blank.
Validation Rules for Faculty
1. Faculty Name minimum 3 characters
Rule Name:

Faculty_Name_Validation

Formula:
LEN(Faculty_Name__c) < 3
Error Message:
Faculty Name must contain at least 3 characters.
2. Faculty ID must be greater than 0
Rule Name:

Faculty_ID_Validation

Formula:
Faculty_ID__c <= 0
Error Message:
Faculty ID must be greater than 0.
3. Salary Validation
Rule Name:

Faculty_Salary_Validation

Formula:
OR(
    Salary__c < 10000,
    Salary__c > 500000
)
Error Message:
Salary must be between 10,000 and 500,000.
4. Department must be selected
Rule Name:

Faculty_Department_Validation

Formula:
ISBLANK(TEXT(Department__c))
Error Message:
Please select Department.
5. Joining Date cannot be future date
Rule Name:

Faculty_JoiningDate_Validation

Formula:
Joining_Date__c > TODAY()
Error Message:
Joining Date cannot be a future date.
Step 3: Faculty ID Unique Constraint

Go to:

Faculty Object → Faculty ID Field

Enable:

✓ Unique
